Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_emm_dma_adr

This register sets the address for eMMC/SD flash transfers to/from memory. Sixty-four-bit operations must be used to access this register. This register is updated by the DMA hardware and can be reloaded by the values placed in the MIO_EMM_DMA_FIFO_ADR.
